    <entry>
      <title>Github+Picgo搭建图床</title>
      <link href="2021/06/04/Github+Picgo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/"/>
      <url>2021/06/04/Github+Picgo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h1><a href="#github" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="github">Github</span></h1><h2><a href="#zhu-ce-zhang-hu" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="zhu-ce-zhang-hu">注册账户</span></h2><p>在<a href="https://github.com/">github</a>首页注册自己的github账户</p><h2><a href="#chuang-jian-cang-ku" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="chuang-jian-cang-ku">创建仓库</span></h2><p>点击右上角的 “+”，选择 New repositories<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/hexopic/img/20210604223002.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/hexopic/img/20210604221849.png"></p><h2><a href="#chuang-jian-token" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="chuang-jian-token">创建token</span></h2><p>此时仓库已经建立，点击右上角头像，在点击setting进入设置；<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/hexopic/img/20210604223401.png"><br>在左侧页面最下找到 Developer settings，点击进入；<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/hexopic/img/20210604223456.png"><br>创建token<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/hexopic/img/20210604223620.png"><br>填写description（随心填），勾选复选框 repo ，接着到页面底部 Generate token 就完成了<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/hexopic/img/20210604223803.png"><br>然后复制生成一串字符 token，这个 token 只出现一次，所以要保存一下。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/hexopic/img/20210604225159.png"></p><h1><a href="#picgo" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="picgo">Picgo</span></h1><h2><a href="#xia-zai" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="xia-zai">下载</span></h2><p>Picgo<a href="https://molunerfinn.com/PicGo/">官网地址</a></p><p>选择最新的releases并选择与自己系统的安装包</p><h2><a href="#pei-zhi" class="header-anchor">#</a><span id="pei-zhi">配置</span></h2><p>打开Picgo，选择图床设置，打开Github图床进行配置<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/hexopic/img/20210605095518.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/hexopic/img/20210605100855.png"></p><ul><li>仓库名 即你的仓库名</li><li>分支名 默认 main</li><li>Token 就是刚刚复制的那一串字符</li><li>存储路径 这个可以填也可以不填，填了的话图片就上传到 git 中 img 这个文件夹</li><li>域名 <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/easn2233/hexopic%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E8%A6%81%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/easn2233/hexopic这个要改一下</a> 格式 <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/[username]/[%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93%E5%90%8D]">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/[username]/[仓库名]</a><br>然后点确定就可以了。</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这里提供一个加速访问图片的方法：CDN加速</span><br><span class="line">将上面的域名改为：</span><br><span class="line">原 https://raw.githubusercontent.com/easn2233/hexopic</span><br><span class="line">现 https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/easn2233/hexopic</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>现在就可以愉快的玩耍拉</p><p>本方案唯一缺点，不能私人。但是考虑到 GitHub 上传的图在列表里没法预览，应该没人会闲着没事翻记录。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 免费白嫖一个图库嘻嘻 - Hexo </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
